SUMMARY:Last Generation: Introduction
LOCATION:5031 St-Denis (métro Laurier)
DESCRIPTION:2026-04-06 19:00:00\n\n5031 St-Denis (métro Laurier)\n\nhttps
 ://www.openstreetmap.org/node/11972883637\n\nDiscussion on the reality of 
 the climate crisis\, civil resistance\, and an introduction to Last Genera
 tion!\n5031 R. Saint-Denis\nTiers Lieu Montreal\nMontreal\nH2J 2L9
